<!-- ================= CHAPTER 1 ================= -->
<h2 id="chapter1">Chapter 1 ‚Äì The Beginning</h2>

<p>The night was unusually quiet, as though the world itself was holding its breath.</p>
<p>Streetlights flickered weakly, casting shadows that stretched far beyond their limits.</p>
<p>She walked alone, her thoughts tangled in memories she had tried to bury.</p>
<p>Every sound felt louder, every movement heavier than before.</p>
<p>The wind whispered secrets she could not yet understand.</p>
<p>Somewhere far away, a clock struck midnight.</p>
<p>Her heart raced as she sensed something unseen watching her.</p>
<p>This was the night everything would change.</p>
<p>The beginning is often silent, unnoticed.</p>

