<!-- ================= CHAPTER 2 ================= -->
<h2 id="chapter2">Chapter 2 ‚Äì The Awakening</h2>

<p>Morning arrived wrapped in pale sunlight.</p>
<p>She awoke with a strange heaviness in her chest.</p>
<p>Dreams clung to her thoughts ‚Äî voices, symbols, a name.</p>
<p>The world outside continued, unaware.</p>
<p>Every reflection looked unfamiliar.</p>
<p>She tried to ignore the feeling, but failed.</p>
<p>The awakening was slow and unavoidable.</p>
<p>Something ancient stirred inside her.</p>
<p>The truth could no longer be denied.</p>

