<!-- ================= CHAPTER 3 ================= -->
<h2 id="chapter3">Chapter 3 ‚Äì Secrets Revealed</h2>

<p>The truth revealed itself piece by piece.</p>
<p>Old books, sealed rooms, and whispered warnings.</p>
<p>Every answer created more questions.</p>
<p>She learned that secrets survive through fear.</p>
<p>Those before her had chosen silence.</p>
<p>Knowledge carried a heavy cost.</p>
<p>She was no longer alone.</p>
<p>The path ahead was dangerous.</p>
<p>But it was clear.</p>

