<!-- ================= END OF NOVEL ================= -->
<h2 id="end">The End</h2>

<p>The journey had reached its conclusion.</p>
<p>Every fear that once ruled her had faded.</p>
<p>She understood now what strength truly meant.</p>
<p>The past no longer controlled her future.</p>
<p>The sun rose gently over a changed world.</p>
<p>This ending was also a beginning.</p>
